title: It's The Return Of The Song Association Game!
description:
The Song Association Game is back! This game has been featured on Elle Magazine’s YouTube page with various celebrities.
Kristin will give us a word, and we have to start singing a song that has that word in it.
Learn more about your ad choices. Visit megaphone.fm/adchoices
